title: Cosmic Queries: Planet Earth
description: StarTalk Radio comes down to Earth as astrophysicist Neil deGrasse Tyson and comic co-host Chuck Nice answer fan questions about our home planet, from how it formed to how it might end.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
